This paper discusses the capabilities of Qu-Prolog for implementing distributed intelligent applications, which falls under the categories of programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses multi-threading and message communication, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). Finally, the paper mentions the support for implementing applications, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
